{
  "texts": [
    "Finally, the evolution of LLM capabilities-particularly their ability to understand and leverage contextual information-may fundamentally alter their differential impact on innovation types over time.",
    "By examining heterogeneous effects across projects with varying levels of user activity and analyzing changes following LLM model improvements, we can assess whether observed patterns represent transient artifacts of current technological limitations or fundamental shifts in innovation economics.",
    "This leads to our third research question: Will the gap between capability and iterative innovation narrow, widen, or remain stable as LLMs' context understanding improves?",
    "The open-source communities of packages for these languages are on GitHub, a platform central to the ecosystem of open-source projects with over 100 million software developers contributing across more than 500 programming languages.",
    "On GitHub, communities organize around code \"repositories\", where contributors can propose and implement code changes through \"commits.\""
  ]
}